CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 1, 1954, pg. 21, reads: "NAACP MEMBERSHIP DRIVE OPENS - The 1954 membership campaign of the Pittsburgh Branch of the NAACP opened Sunday at a meeting at Wesley Center AME Zion Church... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Woman and Marion Bond Jordon holding document, for NAACP membership drive in Wesley Center AME Zion Church
